{"tid":2500701,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實龍門啲嘢食係咪真係咁不堪入口？","createTime":"2021-04-23T00:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T05:15:31.000Z","uid":29784,"like":48,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd0b16bbbc57bc492fba91640add3eb6632501d","tid":2500701,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:50:16.000Z","msg":"見到阿傑佢話就快支持唔落去，今日即刻去幫襯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfG62Y9uAPqXJGa3dfQKGHGdkVZMNYw9u9JXgS4hDByjp?filename=DUWnSCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDUWnSCe.jpg&h=7e78eabb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來諗住食佢個下午茶放題，不過我好大食，驚食窮阿傑，所以最後嗌咗個黯然銷魂飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUsA8bgzLPngoxpuuD65fj2h3oz1tGakdao9EdNxqnM4T?filename=k691oKJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk691oKJ.jpg&h=95d5b6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煲飯好大兜，裝咗一碗俾朋友之後仲有好多，又煎雙蛋又有成三四塊大叉燒，一個人食嘅話應該會好飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n味道方面，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXX63DptfofjJyhoxX7vuSR9NmQaN4bTH9EPMFB5QY9bK?filename=2CMK509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CMK509.jpg&h=7e8d20e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQbq6dBFLEGnRumhFH9SqCaaqEzQmkUt118LG5VtXFWYg?filename=uSLv1zz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuSLv1zz.jpg&h=73e07d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcyY5pPHPvqmYy2dEDnNDE1r2QnG2urwuRtZ6rzgxL6TJ?filename=MEbjas1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEbjas1.jpg&h=cb21ee5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n煎雙蛋煎得好靚，好有蛋香，非精液太陽蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n厚切叉燒又軟稔，半肥瘦適中，大大啖咬落去好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老老實實，有人成日彈龍門啲嘢食好差，但係以平民茶記嚟講，我覺得龍門已經好俾心機去做，絕對對得住個價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家點睇？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />龍門啲嘢食其實唔差<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />龍門啲嘢食其實唔錯"},{"pid":"f0b07f5ac40b9278e892575d8d51694df7d8c3cb","tid":2500701,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:51:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a384951b41ff137257b9ad7fa3a7305ff64507","tid":2500701,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">樓主用舊聞惡意抹黑龍門<br />\n<br />\n（ 突 發 ）龍 門 冰 室 最 後 告 急<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2500662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2500662</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ad4dc82322e9afe086b1aaacee6b56220e82387a","tid":2500701,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b1a384951b41ff137257b9ad7fa3a7305ff64507","tid":2500701,"uid":79793,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T00:51:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">樓主用舊聞惡意抹黑龍門<br />\n<br />\n（ 突 發 ）龍 門 冰 室 最 後 告 急<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2500662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2500662</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20